<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:13:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>反内塔尼亚胡抗议者会见辛本，向他们通报针对总理的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-protesters-meet-with-shin-ben-inform-them-about-protests-against-pm/0000018e-848f-d49b-a3bf-f49fcbec0000</link><description>这次会议被认为非常不寻常，其目的是在总理内塔尼亚胡私人住宅外每周举行的抗议活动中“防止跨越红线”，因为《新本报》官员担心，如果抗议者突破红线，可能会被总理的一名警卫开枪射杀。住宅的周长</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-protesters-meet-with-shin-ben-inform-them-about-protests-against-pm/0000018e-848f-d49b-a3bf-f49fcbec0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡破坏人质交易的机会，国防部长感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-is-sabotaging-chances-for-a-hostage-deal-and-defense-chiefs-are-angry/0000018e-8136-d0d3-a98e-d7ffa0f00000</link><description>据信，哈马斯在加沙扣押的人质中只有 60 至 70 人还活着，但谈判很复杂，并且因总理可疑的借口而陷入僵局</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-is-sabotaging-chances-for-a-hostage-deal-and-defense-chiefs-are-angry/0000018e-8136-d0d3-a98e-d7ffa0f00000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日被绑架的以色列士兵的父母指责内塔尼亚胡政府抛弃他们的儿子，要求与哈马斯达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</link><description>在与总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡会面之前，被哈马斯扣押的以色列士兵的父母声称，内塔尼亚胡“只是在六个月的许多官方请求和媒体请求后才与以色列士兵会面”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日怀疑哈马斯性侵的希伯来大学教授在放弃立场后将复职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</link><description>巴勒斯坦学者 Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授在 10 月 7 日收回对哈马斯性侵犯程度表示怀疑的言论后，希伯来大学撤销了对她的停职。她没有被要求撤销关于以色列正在实施种族灭绝的说法在加沙</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周五早上开始实行夏令时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</link><description>夏令时将于周五凌晨 2 点生效</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:29:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤；以色列军队搜寻袭击者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-israeli-army-searching-for-assailant/0000018e-8435-df27-adee-a6ff9fc90000</link><description>一名枪手向一辆公共汽车和几辆汽车开枪，然后逃离现场。以色列军队正在扫描该地区寻找枪手，伤者已被送往耶路撒冷的医院</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-israeli-army-searching-for-assailant/0000018e-8435-df27-adee-a6ff9fc90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯谈判陷入停滞可能会将与真主党的冲突转变为全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/the-northern-front-heats-back-up-and-israel-readies-for-larger-war-with-hezbollah/0000018e-81a8-d4d2-abfe-a3e9c5630000</link><description>经过数周的相对平静后，北部的紧张局势再次升温，以色列和真主党相互攻击并造成人员伤亡。 ■ 在政治方面，以色列议会准备就征兵豁免问题展开斗争，内塔尼亚胡继续与拜登进行小规模战争，这次“向哈马斯发送消息”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/the-northern-front-heats-back-up-and-israel-readies-for-larger-war-with-hezbollah/0000018e-81a8-d4d2-abfe-a3e9c5630000</guid></item><item><title>爱尔兰准备在国际法院介入南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-live/hezbollah-operatives-among-eight-people-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon/0000018e-829d-d4d2-abfe-a3dd0c720000</link><description>约旦河西岸枪击事件造成三人受伤；以色列军队搜寻袭击者 ■ 真主党特工在以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击中丧生 8 人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军在 Al-Shifa 医院开展行动，称有 200 名恐怖分子被打死 ■ 哈马斯发布了军事部门负责人穆罕默德·戴夫的录音，呼吁阿拉伯世界“向巴勒斯坦进军” ” ■ 白宫表示正在努力重新安排已取消的与以色列代表团有关拉法选项的会议</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 01:18:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-live/hezbollah-operatives-among-eight-people-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon/0000018e-829d-d4d2-abfe-a3dd0c720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法监察员称高等法院法官卡布行为不道德</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</link><description>监察员裁定，查立德·卡布 (Chaled Kabub) 法官未经授权接受媒体采访，违反了法官道德准则，并驳回了卡布 (Kabub) 对他参与涉及其子女的法律纠纷审判的指控的回应。所有针对他的投诉都是由右翼活动家谢伊·格利克（Shay Glick）提交的</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡政府准备招募极端正统派入伍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</link><description>提交请求的截止日期已于周三午夜到期。如果不提交，内阁关于免除极端正统派男子征兵的决定将于周一到期，他们将被征召服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派兵役豁免危机对以色列政治来说是一个地震事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</link><description>即使本杰明·内塔尼亚胡未能通过一项免除所有犹太学院学生服兵役的法律，极端正统派政党也可能会留在政府，但在下一次选举后，他们可能会长期处于反对派状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:56:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯使以色列人失去人性。在以色列，巴勒斯坦人的处境严重非人化。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</link><description>参谋军士。 21 岁的尼西姆·卡奇隆 (Nisim Kachlon) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，在加沙地带南部与恐怖分子的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 18:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 173 天：据报道内塔尼亚胡寻求重新安排他取消的 DC 会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-173-netanyahu-reportedly-trying-to-reschedule-d-c-he-just-canceled/0000018e-80f6-d0d3-a98e-d6ff2b800000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，他取消了华盛顿特区的代表团，以“向哈马斯传递信息” ■ 在华盛顿特区，国防部长加兰特表示，战后以色列和哈马斯都不会统治加沙，必须建立当地的替代方案 ■ 以色列人在黎巴嫩猛烈火箭弹袭击后丧生 ■ 爱尔兰表示将干预南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案 ■ 哈马斯公布了据称是军事首领穆罕默德·代夫的录音 ■ 这是战争开始 173 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-173-netanyahu-reportedly-trying-to-reschedule-d-c-he-just-canceled/0000018e-80f6-d0d3-a98e-d6ff2b800000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这个女人必须将拉比告上以色列最高法院离婚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-woman-had-to-take-the-rabbinate-to-israels-supreme-court-to-get-a-divorce/0000018e-806b-d719-a5ae-ac7b25970000</link><description>在一场涉及三个独立法庭的战斗中，维塔·罗森伯格终于获得了胜利。问题不在于丈夫的顽抗，而在于以色列的首席拉比，后者要求她证明自己的犹太身份才能获得宗教离婚</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:19:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-woman-had-to-take-the-rabbinate-to-israels-supreme-court-to-get-a-divorce/0000018e-806b-d719-a5ae-ac7b25970000</guid></item><item><title>警察搜查参加反政府抗议的以色列人的卧室</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/police-ransack-bedroom-of-israeli-who-participated-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</link><description>警方在房间里捣毁后没有找到他们要找的东西，但最终逮捕了这名活动人士，并试图将她拘留五天。 “我们作为激进主义的行动空间正在缩小，”她说</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/police-ransack-bedroom-of-israeli-who-participated-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫：内塔尼亚胡决定“重新安排”以色列代表团赴美参与拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡似乎推翻了之前的声明，即在美国决定不否决联合国安理会停火决议后，他将以色列代表团撤回华盛顿，以此向哈马斯发出“信息”，即它不能依赖国际压力</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 16:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国经济学家、诺贝尔奖获得者丹尼尔·卡尼曼去世，享年 90 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</link><description>卡尼曼与阿莫斯·特沃斯基联合开展的将心理学见解融入经济学的开创性工作为他赢得了 2002 年诺贝尔奖。他是内塔尼亚胡政府司法改革的直言不讳的批评者</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</guid></item><item><title>被停职的以色列政府发言人埃隆·利维正式被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</link><description>在与英国外交部长发生推特争议后，一名政府官员表示，利维“偏离了以色列的信息，采取了太多自由”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙受伤的以色列歌手拒绝点燃独立日火炬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</link><description>演员、歌手兼以色列国防军预备役军人伊丹·阿梅迪拒绝了这一请求，称其他人比他更值得，他希望“由于我写下的文字，而不是由于战争英雄主义，他将被授予点燃火炬的功绩”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</guid></item></channel></rss>